00:55:36.351 --> 00:55:42.000
" Last night, I went to the church and I went to a prayer group meeting.

00:55:42.000 --> 00:55:48.560
And in this prayer, I saw a golden path that looked like cobblestone golden bricks that were laid out.

00:55:58.080 --> 00:55:58.343
But at the end of this path, I saw this massive demon.

00:56:04.040 --> 00:56:04.260
And this demon was completely blacked out like it was a shadow.

00:56:10.960 --> 00:56:11.349
And it was at the end of this path.

00:56:16.160 --> 00:56:18.464
On the other side of this demon was a glorious church, a staircase.

00:56:20.000 --> 00:56:20.495
I saw all this beautiful glory.

00:56:25.680 --> 00:56:27.290
But the devil was trying to block the people from getting to where they needed to get through the glory.

00:56:35.176 --> 00:56:35.552
On one side of them was war.

00:56:35.552 --> 00:56:39.533
I saw great war in the East.

00:56:39.533 --> 00:56:43.040
I saw great war on our East Coast.

00:56:43.040 --> 00:56:48.644
I saw civil war, trouble, great trouble on his right, which would be the West.

00:56:56.547 --> 00:56:57.160
There was drought, there was famine, there was pestilence, there was all kinds of...

00:57:07.270 --> 00:57:07.560
it looked like the Dust Bowl was all on his right.

00:57:07.560 --> 00:57:09.352
It was very dry.

00:57:09.352 --> 00:57:14.515
It looked in the vision like it was very hot.

00:57:26.740 --> 00:57:27.025
But as I looked down toward the ground, there were babies all around that were trying to be aborted.

00:57:33.280 --> 00:57:33.687
And the Lord said, "This is not physical abortion.

00:57:43.298 --> 00:57:44.844
This is spiritual people aborting their call, saying, 'I don't want to do this anymore,' and falling away and not coming to the church and not being a part of the outpouring.

00:57:44.844 --> 00:57:48.160
" Each baby was wrapped in a beautiful garment.

00:57:48.160 --> 00:57:54.903
Each baby, the gifts and callings of the Lord without repentance.

00:57:54.903 --> 00:57:58.684
The gifts are there; God doesn't take them back away from you.

00:57:58.684 --> 00:58:22.147
If you're talented and can sing and lead worship, you can use those gifts and the talents that he gives us to be like Celine Dion or whoever and use the gifts and the talents for the world or you can use them for him.

00:58:22.147 --> 00:58:40.600
But he doesn't go well because when you're born with a gift that can sing like an Andrea Bocelli, he doesn't say, 'I'm not going to allow you to sing for the world and sing this; I want you to only sing for the church.

00:58:40.600 --> 00:58:50.297
' He is a merciful God and he gives us free will—all the gifts and the talents God gives us—but he doesn't beat you in the head with it.

00:59:00.053 --> 00:59:00.262
I saw each one of these babies.

00:59:00.262 --> 00:59:02.680
They had stripes on their gowns.

00:59:02.680 --> 00:59:04.975
They had beautiful colors; it looked like silk.

00:59:09.672 --> 00:59:09.936
It was beautiful, vibrant colors, and they were each wrapped, and each one had a gift.

00:59:11.950 --> 00:59:31.949
But as offense towards churches, as people aborted themselves from being in a congregation where they were meant to be—and they left when God had assigned you to be there, God had assigned you to be at that place and you said, 'I'm not going there anymore'—you are that missing puzzle piece for that congregation.

00:59:31.949 --> 00:59:40.590
If God calls you to a place and you say, 'I'm done.

00:59:53.320 --> 00:59:53.560
I'm out of here,' and you're a baby, you aborted yourself.

01:00:09.080 --> 01:00:09.440
You aborted what you could have become.

01:00:09.440 --> 01:00:14.440
A baby stays a baby if you don't grow up.

01:00:14.440 --> 01:00:22.430
And the babies were lying right there, crying all around, and that devil was blocking and causing havoc on the road to glory so people would be derailed.

01:00:22.430 --> 01:00:24.620
Does this make sense, what I'm saying?

01:00:37.200 --> 01:00:37.850
They would be derailed off of what God's original assignment was for you to do.

01:00:37.850 --> 01:00:41.827
God doesn't give you a second assignment until you finish the first assignment.

01:00:41.827 --> 01:00:44.223
Go back to what God originally told you to do.

01:00:44.691 --> 01:00:53.328
You say, 'Well, he hasn't told me to do anything else,' because you haven't been obedient with the first thing he told you to do.

01:00:53.328 --> 01:00:58.213
Obey what he told you to do, and you'll get letter B.

01:00:59.360 --> 01:01:06.480
It's like A, B, C, D; but you can't go from A to B to C to D until you've been obedient with A.

01:01:06.480 --> 01:01:11.333
There's an order all the way to XYZ.

01:01:14.627 --> 01:01:16.320
The alphabet is the way it is, but it's just an illustration.

01:01:16.320 --> 01:01:19.533
Mathematics would probably be better to do it like that.

01:01:19.533 --> 01:01:24.933
You have to learn addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division to get to algebra.

01:01:24.933 --> 01:01:30.550
You don't just start algebra until you learn the basics of everything else.

01:01:33.829 --> 01:01:37.920
The point is that people think, 'Why am I still dwarfed in my belief?

01:01:37.920 --> 01:01:41.960
Why am I still dwarfed in my faith?

01:01:41.960 --> 01:01:43.080
Why have I not grown up?

01:01:43.080 --> 01:01:53.890
' Because a plant does not grow well unless it's in the soil God planted you in.

01:01:55.370 --> 01:02:00.600
I cannot put a palm tree in Nebraska because God didn't design a palm tree to grow in Colorado or Nebraska.

01:02:00.600 --> 01:02:04.657
He designed it to be in Miami, Florida, or wherever.

01:02:04.657 --> 01:02:05.970
Do you understand?

01:02:05.970 --> 01:02:13.031
I cannot expect a beautiful evergreen cedar tree to grow on the beach.

01:02:13.031 --> 01:02:15.110
It doesn't work that way.

01:02:15.110 --> 01:02:27.720
And so God has a specific place for you to be so that you grow your fruit and you grow your tree.

01:02:27.720 --> 01:02:31.815
your life, your spiritual life, and I put you in this place.

01:02:31.815 --> 01:02:37.790
But you are a baby, and a baby doesn't know where it's supposed to be.

01:02:37.790 --> 01:02:39.754
A baby just needs to yield.

01:02:39.754 --> 01:02:41.395
I just go, "It's okay, honey.

01:02:41.395 --> 01:02:42.135
I'll help you.

01:02:49.165 --> 01:02:49.360
" And he's gracious and merciful.

01:02:49.360 --> 01:02:58.467
But as I saw all these babies at the feet, the devil was laughing about it because he felt like he had the upper hand.

01:02:58.467 --> 01:03:01.320
"See, I've blocked them from getting to where they're supposed to be.

01:03:01.320 --> 01:03:05.088
" He was doing everything he could.

01:03:05.088 --> 01:03:15.258
As I was praying from the throne, I saw a shaft of light pierce that demonic spirit that looked almost like a bullet wound.

01:03:15.258 --> 01:03:24.880
And the glory of the Lord started to penetrate that demonic spirit, and it started to spread.

01:03:33.711 --> 01:03:39.293
The light started to disintegrate the center of this demonic being's chest by prayer, by the warriors, and all of a sudden that demonic spirit started to weaken.

01:03:39.293 --> 01:03:42.590
And the dark form of great black, which was—here's a color chart.

01:03:42.590 --> 01:03:44.827
Braden always was using this.

01:03:50.720 --> 01:04:00.370
This dark color, it was as black as molasses, the darkest black you could see, became a little gray, then became a little grayer, and his skin, whatever you want to call it, started to be see-through.

01:04:11.216 --> 01:04:11.472
The babies that were on the ground started going back to where they were supposed to go.

01:04:12.680 --> 01:04:18.840
And I saw an adding of a supply of unoffended, repentant Christians that said, "I sell out to the Lord.

01:04:18.840 --> 01:04:29.966
I'm sorry I missed it," and got back on the right path to go to the glory.

01:04:29.966 --> 01:04:35.240
And they put themselves where God had originally put them.

01:04:35.240 --> 01:04:39.680
They went back to where they were supposed to be.

01:04:39.680 --> 01:04:42.250
And they dealt with the offense.

01:04:42.250 --> 01:04:43.810
They dealt with the hurt.

01:04:43.810 --> 01:04:45.829
They dealt with the ego.

01:04:59.549 --> 01:04:59.823
They dealt with the pride.

01:05:08.745 --> 01:05:09.570
And they said, "Father, I yield to you.

01:05:09.570 --> 01:05:17.360
I'm going back to what you called me to do.

01:05:17.360 --> 01:05:20.720
Not my will, but yours be done.

01:05:20.720 --> 01:05:25.994
" Because the willing and obedient will eat the good of the land.

01:05:32.507 --> 01:05:32.853
You say, "I don't understand why I'm not eating the good of the land, Brandon.

01:05:32.853 --> 01:05:36.263
Why are my finances struggling so bad?

01:05:36.263 --> 01:05:38.320
Why is all this?

01:05:38.320 --> 01:05:46.576
" Because you weren't willing and you weren't obedient to what God had told you to do.

01:05:46.576 --> 01:05:53.200
Go back to what God has told you to do.

01:06:08.150 --> 01:06:08.455
You say, "Well, I have all this.

01:06:08.455 --> 01:06:12.490
I felt like I was always called to the ministry.

01:06:28.340 --> 01:06:28.680
I felt like I was called to women's ministry.

01:06:28.680 --> 01:06:43.903
I felt like I was going to do this, and I never saw the full manifestation of it because you derailed yourself because you didn't stay on what God had told you to do.

01:06:43.903 --> 01:06:49.185
" Go back to the ABCs and 123s to learn to get to algebra.

01:06:49.185 --> 01:06:50.984
"Well, I'm big enough.

01:06:50.984 --> 01:06:55.500
I don't need all that.

01:06:55.500 --> 01:06:56.720
" No, no, no.

01:06:56.720 --> 01:07:02.985
If you don't know your addition and your multiplication and all this, you'll never understand algebra.

01:07:14.777 --> 01:07:14.994
I don't care.

01:07:24.846 --> 01:07:25.143
"Well, you know what?

01:07:34.410 --> 01:07:34.765
I think I can solve it.

01:07:34.765 --> 01:07:42.360
" You're never going to solve it.

01:07:42.360 --> 01:07:54.021
You're never going to solve algebra.

01:08:34.787 --> 01:08:35.860
You have to go back to what God had called you to do.

01:08:35.860 --> 01:08:42.506
Don't dwarf your roots.

01:08:42.506 --> 01:09:17.120
A tree that's planted in the wrong soil and plucked up so many times never develops like it should.

01:09:17.120 --> 01:09:25.855
The taproot goes down deep.

01:10:19.360 --> 01:10:54.800
And if you keep messing and pulling the taproot and doing all the things, you'll never become what God originally told you you would be because you haven't been obedient with what he asked you to do in the first place.

01:11:20.795 --> 01:11:24.270
And as I saw that devil start to disintegrate through prayer and intercession, I saw his parting of it.

01:11:24.280 --> 01:11:45.720
But I saw what was a blinder on those babies start going and bringing the babies back.

01:11:50.232 --> 01:12:09.467
And it goes with what the Lord said, "Be patient with my babies, for you were once a baby.

01:12:09.467 --> 01:12:13.640
Be patient with the ones that are coming in, for you were once a baby.

01:12:14.486 --> 01:12:16.858
" There was more to the vision.

01:12:17.116 --> 01:12:20.540
It was about some things the Lord was showing me privately.

01:12:21.745 --> 01:12:28.183
I won't bring all that because you'll say I'm bragging.

01:12:28.183 --> 01:12:41.629
But the Lord said to me specifically some things directly to Diana and I in that.

01:12:55.040 --> 01:12:55.570
And it was really encouraging.

01:12:55.570 --> 01:13:06.893
But I want to say to you, don't be offended.

01:13:06.893 --> 01:13:24.647
Go back to, like I told you, the Bait of Satan.

01:13:24.647 --> 01:14:20.110
The devil will use all these things against you to derail what God has called you to do because of your flesh.

01:14:20.120 --> 01:14:26.700
I'm just trying to help.

01:14:34.958 --> 01:14:39.440
And as I saw that, I saw churches starting to explode because people say, "I'm not going back.

01:14:39.440 --> 01:14:42.520
I'll just watch online.

01:14:42.520 --> 01:14:45.974
I'm going to do this.

01:14:45.974 --> 01:14:48.320
They did this to me.

01:14:48.320 --> 01:14:55.246
I'm upset; I'm not ever going to step foot back into a church again.

01:14:55.246 --> 01:14:56.980
" Bunch of hypocrites.

01:14:56.980 --> 01:15:00.500
I'm telling you, we're all saved by grace.

01:15:00.500 --> 01:15:03.973
We all have something we're overcoming.

01:15:03.973 --> 01:15:09.875
There isn't one of us better than the other.

01:15:09.875 --> 01:15:25.060
I don't care who you are.

01:15:43.077 --> 01:15:44.235
You could be the one that would be closest to Peter walking on the water.

01:15:44.235 --> 01:15:59.477
But you still have issues because Peter denied him.

01:15:59.477 --> 01:16:33.680
I want you to understand that all of us have sinned and fallen short of the glory—all of us, even Peter.

01:16:50.171 --> 01:16:50.469
And Peter was awesome, obviously.

01:17:29.840 --> 01:17:30.067
I mean, seriously, he was walking on the water.

01:17:50.085 --> 01:17:50.330
I mean, he was cool.

01:17:50.330 --> 01:17:55.777
I want to be cool; I want to be buddies with him.

01:17:55.777 --> 01:18:00.040
Well, let's watch him walk on the water, you know?

01:18:00.040 --> 01:18:04.766
But the same man denied him, and Jesus forgave him.

01:18:04.766 --> 01:18:25.126
So even on our best day, you know, we're all just sick sinners saved by grace.

01:18:30.060 --> 01:18:30.305
Thank God for his blood, ladies and gentlemen.

01:18:50.880 --> 01:18:51.107
But I'm trying to tell you, there's coming a revival.

01:18:51.107 --> 01:18:52.240
There's coming a shaking.

01:18:58.800 --> 01:18:59.058
And you bring a piece to that church.

01:18:59.058 --> 01:19:06.100
You bring a piece to where you were supposed to be that nobody else is going to fulfill because he assigned you to be there.

01:19:06.100 --> 01:19:14.496
He may bring somebody else along that has something similar, maybe because you might be that hard-headed.

01:19:14.496 --> 01:19:21.560
But the bottom line is that you have what it takes.

01:19:21.920 --> 01:19:23.354
You have that gift.

01:19:24.771 --> 01:19:25.480
You have that puzzle piece.

01:19:32.069 --> 01:19:32.343
And that puzzle piece, you were made to fit that perfect puzzle.

01:19:38.500 --> 01:19:38.750
Because of you, you make a whole picture.

01:19:43.510 --> 01:19:43.720
And they go, 'You know what?

01:19:43.720 --> 01:19:48.440
Without that centerpiece, that whole thing would have been messed up.

01:20:05.920 --> 01:20:06.640
But thank God you came back.

01:20:06.640 --> 01:20:12.840
' So I just encourage you: seek your heart and where God wants you today.

01:20:12.840 --> 01:20:15.880
Ask the Father, 'Forgive me.

01:20:15.880 --> 01:20:16.566
Help me.

01:20:16.566 --> 01:20:24.308
' If I need to go back and make things right, if I need to do this, Father, search me and know me.

01:20:24.308 --> 01:20:27.786
It may be that God moved you on.

01:20:27.786 --> 01:20:30.830
Maybe, I don't know.

01:20:30.840 --> 01:20:37.850
But always inquire of the Lord.

01:20:37.850 --> 01:20:47.880
There have been a lot of big decisions that I've had to make in the last 48 hours.

01:20:56.720 --> 01:20:56.885
And the major thing that Diana, my wife, always said to me: 'Brandon, have you inquired of the Lord?

01:20:57.875 --> 01:21:01.096
Have you sat and made the decisions based on him or out of just what you think or fear?

01:21:01.096 --> 01:21:03.260
' Did you inquire of the Lord?

01:21:03.260 --> 01:21:05.680
Did you fast and pray before you make major decisions today?

01:21:13.149 --> 01:21:18.089
And I say, 'Yeah, I need to.

01:21:18.089 --> 01:21:20.844
' So I did today.

01:21:21.831 --> 01:21:21.996
I did Sunday.

01:21:24.450 --> 01:21:24.620
I prayed.

01:21:32.945 --> 01:21:33.240
And so it's amazing when you take that time.

01:21:34.296 --> 01:21:44.337
And there was this dear sister—and I'm not promoting her channel because I don't know what else she said—but the Lord said, 'I want you to go and listen to this lady.

01:21:44.337 --> 01:21:56.376
' She was a witch and she got born again, and her channel was about hexes and vexes, talking about the occult coming against Christians and the symptoms and things like that.

01:21:56.376 --> 01:21:58.320
And she said, "I got born again.

01:21:59.209 --> 01:22:11.855
I was in the occult, and she was talking about the blood of Jesus and all these things, but I'm very cautious of what I'm listening to.

01:22:13.760 --> 01:22:22.773
I filter it a lot because I'm like, 'Okay, but why did you point this out to me?

01:22:22.773 --> 01:22:29.155
' And there's so many things that this lady said that helped.

01:22:30.960 --> 01:22:47.820
And I sat there and I went, 'Okay, you realize what's coming against you over the course of the days,' and you go, 'This is not normal, the things that are happening,' and then you realize who you are in Christ.

01:22:47.820 --> 01:22:51.385
Always keep yourself polished, always keep yourself full.

01:22:51.385 --> 01:22:54.656
Be filled with and controlled by the Holy Ghost.

01:22:54.656 --> 01:22:57.498
So I hope that helped you.

01:23:03.674 --> 01:23:04.086
That was a little bit extra, but the Lord said to share it, and that's what I saw last night.

01:23:04.086 --> 01:23:13.000
And I'm so thankful that he talks to me and leads me, telling the people, 'Get ready.

01:23:13.000 --> 01:23:15.920
A great revival is right at hand.

01:23:15.920 --> 01:23:19.440
And it's time for people to grow up.

01:23:19.440 --> 01:23:21.400
Don't be babies anymore.

01:23:21.400 --> 01:23:23.520
Yeah, people offend you.

01:23:23.520 --> 01:23:33.743
Yeah, people talk trash about you, especially me—run you down, run your family down, run all kinds of things down.

01:23:33.743 --> 01:23:37.512
But when all there is to do is stand, stand therefore.

01:23:37.512 --> 01:23:37.696
They can accuse you.

01:23:37.696 --> 01:23:40.240
They can throw rocks at you.

01:23:40.240 --> 01:23:42.543
They can do all these things to you.

01:23:42.543 --> 01:23:46.907
But the bottom line is that the Lord said, 'Fear me, not them.

01:23:46.907 --> 01:23:55.613
You'll stand before me and give account to everything I've asked you to do, Brandon.

01:23:55.613 --> 01:23:58.080
Don't worry about how many rocks they throw at you.

01:23:58.080 --> 01:24:03.416
To be absent from the body is to be present with the Lord.

01:24:03.416 --> 01:24:06.634
' Brandon, they're always going to hate you.

01:24:06.634 --> 01:24:10.800
They're going to hate you for my sake.

01:24:10.800 --> 01:24:12.373
Do you understand?

01:24:12.373 --> 01:24:16.583
You don't wrestle against flesh and blood.

01:24:16.583 --> 01:24:27.912
You wrestle against the principalities and the powers and the spiritual wickedness in high places.

01:24:53.920 --> 01:24:56.090
You're not wrestling against the people coming against you.

01:24:56.090 --> 01:25:03.280
It's the devil that's inside of them persecuting you.

01:25:20.895 --> 01:25:21.230
And they go, 'Well, we're doing it all for the cause of Christ.

01:25:21.230 --> 01:25:22.235
' No.

01:25:22.235 --> 01:25:23.960
The Pharisees did.

01:25:23.960 --> 01:25:27.560
They persecuted Jesus, too.

01:25:27.560 --> 01:25:49.440
But I look at when people persecute you the most, you've touched a nerve when it comes to praying for the things you're praying for, especially online—praying for our president and lifting him up on a day-to-day basis that he finishes this war and he liberates the people of Cuba.

01:25:49.440 --> 01:25:58.810
And you're lifting him up on your shoulders and you're carrying him across the threshold of the end zone.

01:25:58.810 --> 01:26:01.949
He can't do it on his own.

01:26:07.623 --> 01:26:09.420
And that was the Lord telling me.

01:26:09.420 --> 01:26:11.240
He said, 'Brandon, you must help.

01:26:11.240 --> 01:26:13.260
'" You must intercede for this man.

01:26:13.260 --> 01:26:15.080
Pray for the churches of America.

01:26:15.080 --> 01:26:16.080
Pray for midterms.

01:26:16.080 --> 01:26:17.760
Benny Johnson had a video.

01:26:17.760 --> 01:26:21.613
I commented it's going to take a miracle to win the Senate.

01:26:30.813 --> 01:26:31.000
Do you understand?

01:26:34.329 --> 01:26:38.840
I truly believe in my heart, from everything I keep seeing, we will lose the Senate and keep the House.

01:26:38.840 --> 01:26:43.490
But we need both, and we need to get that bill passed.

01:26:43.490 --> 01:26:44.730
What is it?

01:26:48.823 --> 01:26:49.131
The Voting Bill Act, the Save America Act.

01:26:49.131 --> 01:26:51.640
Why are we not voting on this?

01:26:51.640 --> 01:26:54.315
What's wrong with you?

01:26:54.315 --> 01:26:55.020
Pam Bondi.

01:26:55.020 --> 01:26:57.587
They're talking about Pam Bondi losing her job.

01:27:01.783 --> 01:27:02.091
We're going to replace her because...

01:27:02.091 --> 01:27:07.371
I told you she had a bounty on her head for $50,000.

01:27:20.960 --> 01:27:23.320
I saw it.

01:27:34.893 --> 01:27:35.367
The Lord said her life is in danger.

01:27:42.034 --> 01:27:46.825
And I'm sure they've gotten to her, saying, 'You either shut up and don't do these things, or we're going to make sure you are swimming with the fishes.

01:27:46.825 --> 01:27:48.920
' Do you understand?

01:27:48.920 --> 01:28:00.987
So now Trump's saying that he's going to remove her and put some brown-headed girl in there, is what the rumors I'm hearing.

01:28:00.987 --> 01:28:02.736
Well, maybe he should.

01:28:07.240 --> 01:28:12.410
If she hasn't got a backbone like a crowbar anymore, put somebody who will prosecute and do the things that need to be done for America.

01:28:12.410 --> 01:28:16.740
We need that Save America Act done this week.

01:28:29.984 --> 01:28:30.252
We need it right now.

01:28:30.252 --> 01:28:32.220
